---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="Research & Methodology - Instrumetriq"
  description="Learn about Instrumetriq's research methodology and approach to sentiment data collection"
>
  <article>
    <h1>Research & Methodology</h1>
    
    <section>
      <h2>Overview</h2>
      <p>
        Instrumetriq employs a systematic approach to collecting sentiment data from social media platforms.
        Our methodology prioritizes ethical data collection, user privacy, and data quality.
      </p>
    </section>
    
    <section>
      <h2>Data Collection Approach</h2>
      <p>
        Our data collection process follows established best practices for social media research:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Compliance with platform Terms of Service</li>
        <li>Respect for user privacy and consent</li>
        <li>Anonymization and de-identification of personal information</li>
        <li>Transparent documentation of collection methods</li>
      </ul>
    </section>
    
    <section>
      <h2>Sentiment Analysis Framework</h2>
      <p>
        Details about our sentiment analysis methodology will be published here as the project develops.
      </p>
    </section>
    
    <section>
      <h2>Ethics & Privacy</h2>
      <p>
        We are committed to ethical research practices and protecting user privacy throughout
        the data collection and analysis process.
      </p>
    </section>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  article {
    max-width: 800px;
  }
  
  h1 {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
  }
  
  section {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2xl);
  }
  
  h2 {
    margin-top: var(--space-xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }
</style>
